www.eqprices.com <http://www.eqprices.com> is also down too. It is really
sad all the work these guys have put into their web site and then can't
operate self-sufficient with the fall of the ".com" economy. NO ONE can
expect these sites to operate with the owners paying upwards of $1k a month
to keep it running.
